Privacy Policy
Flower Hotel & Resort ("we", "us", "our") operates the Flower Hotel Direct Sales messaging application.

Last updated: June 16, 2026

Information We Collect
When you send a message to our Facebook Page or Instagram account, we collect your sender ID and the timestamp of your first message. We do not collect your name, email, or personal profile information.

How We Use Information
We use this information solely to track and respond to customer inquiries about hotel reservations and services. We assign your message to the appropriate staff member based on the time of contact.

Data Retention
Conversation records are retained for operational purposes and are accessible only to authorized hotel staff.

Third-Party Services
We use Meta (Facebook/Instagram) Messenger platform to receive messages. Meta's own privacy policy applies to your use of their platforms.

